41:56.960 --> 41:57.760
Sebelah sini.

42:14.620 --> 42:20.490
[Yan Ling]

42:27.960 --> 42:29.220
Sudah kubilang, 'kan?

42:30.440 --> 42:32.170
Kesabaran itu sangat penting.

42:32.400 --> 42:33.200
Benar tidak?

42:40.550 --> 42:42.680
